featureModel.name: spl
featureModel.content:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="ASCII"?>
<feature:DEFeatureModel xmi:version="2.0" xmlns:xmi="http://www.omg.org/XMI" xmlns:feature="http://deltaecore.org/feature/1.0">
  <rootFeature minCardinality="1" maxCardinality="1" name="EmergencyCall">
    <groups minCardinality="3" maxCardinality="4">
      <features minCardinality="1" maxCardinality="1" name="Base">
        <groups minCardinality="1" maxCardinality="1">
          <features maxCardinality="1" name="eCall"/>
          <features maxCardinality="1" name="EraGlonass"/>
        </groups>
      </features>
      <features minCardinality="1" maxCardinality="1" name="Languages">
        <groups minCardinality="1" maxCardinality="1">
          <features maxCardinality="1" name="Russian"/>
          <features maxCardinality="1" name="EU_Languages"/>
        </groups>
      </features>
      <features minCardinality="1" maxCardinality="1" name="GNSS">
        <groups minCardinality="1" maxCardinality="2">
          <features maxCardinality="1" name="GPS"/>
          <features maxCardinality="1" name="Glonass"/>
        </groups>
      </features>
      <features maxCardinality="1" name="Diagnostic"/>
    </groups>
  </rootFeature>
</feature:DEFeatureModel>
